{"tid":1385233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家狗鐵日日都延誤暫停封站 係咪要罰錢?","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:57:00.000Z","uid":92565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75509540778bf1a8b6d5383b29005b1a93be88e4","tid":1385233,"uid":92565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/tp/papers/tp20190426cb4-766-4-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Fpapers%2Ftp20190426cb4-766-4-c.pdf&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=9a1b2e7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/tp/papers/tp20190426cb4-766-4-c.pdf</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">列車服務延誤包括港鐵公司控制範圍內因機件故障或人為因素導致的服務延誤及暫停，「豁免事故」(即並非港鐵公司所引致的事故，如乘客行為和惡劣天氣等)則不會納入服務表現安排。</code></pre><br />\n今日算係「豁免事故」 咁個個星期封站唔停站嗰啲呢？ 又使唔使罰錢？邊個判斷？"},{"pid":"73cff95b5d15d558e1551451a52471976fc875c0","tid":1385233,"uid":92565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36967d2fdff0980270d8c1995d0b73ed5018018e","tid":1385233,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"今日唔會罰錢 係人為事故"},{"pid":"af6e3a54c087edaec32cbd83853399986e807a6e","tid":1385233,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"警方要求"},{"pid":"74ab6e4deaddcfb6a7dcd907369284736799fd3a","tid":1385233,"uid":92565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6e3a54c087edaec32cbd83853399986e807a6e","tid":1385233,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"警方要求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"地鐵冇得say no? 如果有 算唔算佢引致?"},{"pid":"40b14728335763778d9acdf7983d82589db1852e","tid":1385233,"uid":110851,"li